						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">mattmatteh wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">what color is drawn when the ppu is off ? (sprites and background is disabled)</div>
<br />
<br />$3F00
<br />
<br /><em>Unless</em> the PPU address is currently $3Fxx or any mirrored region -- in which case the color drawn is what is stored at the current PPU address (when PPU_addr = $3F04, color $3F04 is drawn)</div>

