						<div class="postbody">In case there's any question remaining:
<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">int entry = 0;<br />if &#40; &#40;vaddr &amp; 0x3F00&#41; == 0x3F00 &#41;<br />&#123;<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; entry = vaddr &amp; 0x1F;<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; if &#40; &#40;entry &amp; 0x13&#41; == 0x10 &#41;<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; entry ^= 0x10; // mirrored entries<br />&#125;<br />color = palette &#91;entry&#93;;</div></div>

